title: Introduction to Superstarch
content: A product derived from corn starch, called Superstarch, is used to improve athletic performance. It is produced by Generation UCAN. It is suggested that consuming Superstarch is better than consuming Gatorade, Powerade, goo, gel, or other 'sports nutrition' products. To understand why, it's important to know how these products work.

title: Superstarch vs Other Sports Nutrition Products
content: Superstarch is referred to as 'superior technology'. If Superstarch is the latest iPhone, all other sports nutrition products are rotary phones. They simply donâ€™t belong in the same sentence. Superstarch is a step-function improvement over all existing products.

title: Origins and Impact of Superstarch
content: This technology, while originally developed to save the lives of children with a very rare genetic disorder, is going to revolutionize sports nutrition as we know it.
